caption.p: Gas chromatography-flame ionization detector (GC–FID) representative chromatogram from 0 to 240 min distillation time with α-thujene ( 1), α-pinene ( 2), camphene ( 3), sabinene ( 4), β-pinene ( 5), myrcene ( 6), α-phellandrene ( 7), 3-carene ( 8), α-terpinene ( 9), p-cymene ( 10), limonene ( 11), γ-terpinene ( 12), terpinolene ( 13), terpinen-4-ol ( 14), safrole ( 15), and myristicin ( 16) indicated.
